column5: Another year older, another year wiser  Happy Birthday Sweetie!!  Joey
Holy crap he is older again soon we will have to have a ramp installed to get him in the boat. Have a great B-Day Paul I know your with Joey so its gonna be great.

HEY Paulucci! Happy bird day eh? Think after a few thousand tries you can pierce the quarter? Maybe Dan Boone can help you wit dat!  Also, your tents have been in the wet for a week...they need a blow dry... fairies can't do it. Need a recomendation?  You have the best day my friend.  edit:  What am I saying... you already have Joey so you're having a great life!
All the Best Paul...  Are you goin' to get Joey to take you for a ride in your wagon?
Happy Birthday Paul, have a great one.
Yup - soon have to hook up a wheel chair to haul the wagon around. Hope ya have a great one Paul.
Happy Birthday and Best Fishes to Paul!!!
Have a great day Paul.  Now go and sit and watch the Montreal race with a cold one.
Thanks for the well wishes.  been drying and cleaning the boat and camp gear all day.

Wiser Rye.... or Bud"wiser"??  regardless happy birthday bud!  I still remember you singing on the ice... while dancing away....  "Im so witty! ohhh so pretty... I'm so witty and pretty and....."  LOL good times bud!  Have a good one...  G
All the 'Best' today buddy,and many,many more to ya........TC and tight lines.....Chuck.....
Think that merits a frostie in your name brah..  Happy Birthday!
Kind of late on this one but hope you had a great day..... Happy Birthday Paul
Hope your day was GREAT fella !
Hope you had a great day Paul.
Belated Bud, I'll give you the year older part.
Happy Belated Birthday Paul!  Hope it was great!
